OL,3,CHow will Reeves' budget reset and
OL,4,Cremake Britain?
OL,6,FAnd almost exactly the opposite of the
OL,7,Fright-wing Brexiters' utopia is coming
OL,8,Ffrom the newish Labour government,
OL,9,Fwith tomorrow's budget - which will
OL,10,Freconstruct and reset the British
OL,11,Fstate and British economy in a form
OL,12,Fthat would be an anathema to more-or-
OL,13,Fless all Brexiters on the right.
OL,15,FThere is zero chance that the
OL,16,FChancellor Rachel Reeves will frame
OL,17,Fher historic budget as the first
OL,18,Fambitious attempt to remake Britain
OL,19,Fafter Brexit.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/13
