OL,3,CHow will Reeves' budget reset and
OL,4,Cremake Britain?
OL,6,FBut that is what it will be, because
OL,7,Fit will endeavour to achieve three
OL,8,Fvery big things, by exploiting the
OL,9,Fmoney-raising and allocative power of
OL,10,Fthe state rather than via the
OL,11,Fdistributive mechanisms of the market
OL,12,Fand private sector.
OL,14,FThese are the three main budget themes:
OL,16,FThis is how Reeves hopes to reassure
OL,17,Finvestors and avoid fiscal shocks.
OL,19,FIt in turn necessitates an increase in
OL,20,Ftaxes to the tune of up to #40 billion
OL,21,Fa year, which could be a modern record.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/13
