OL,3,CHow will Reeves' budget reset and
OL,4,Cremake Britain?
OL,6,FIt's an excuse she and Starmer can use
OL,7,Fonly once, and only now.
OL,9,FWhich is why the budget will announce
OL,10,Fa lot of potentially unpopular and
OL,11,Fpainful measures, in the hope and
OL,12,Fexpectation that they won't have to
OL,13,Fcome back and ask voters for a lot
OL,14,Fmore in additional taxes between now
OL,15,Fand the next election.
OL,17,FThat said, some of what they will
OL,18,Funveil will be described by economists
OL,19,Fand tax experts as sub-optimal.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/13
