OL,3,CHow will Reeves' budget reset and
OL,4,Cremake Britain?
OL,6,FFor example, their plan to claw back
OL,7,FJeremy Hunt's #20 billion in national
OL,8,Finsurance (NI) cuts for employees via
OL,9,Fa #20 billion rise in NI for employers
OL,10,Fis a fiscal prompt for the words
OL,11,F"daft" and "brush".
OL,13,FIt would have been far cleaner and
OL,14,Fwould have posed less of a risk to
OL,15,Femployment to simply reverse the
OL,16,Femployee NI cut. But Starmer's
OL,17,Fmanifesto pledge not to tamper with NI
OL,18,Frates precluded that.
