OL,3,CHow will Reeves' budget reset and
OL,4,Cremake Britain?
OL,6,FSimilarly there was a strong case for
OL,7,Freforming capital gains tax, but
OL,8,Fapparently HMRC lacked the resource to
OL,9,Fproperly work through the consequences
OL,10,Fof root-and-branch change, so instead
OL,11,FReeves has opted for the path of least
OL,12,Fresistance, via an increase in the
OL,13,Fbasic rate from 20% to around 24%.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/13
