OL,3,CHow will Reeves' budget reset and
OL,4,Cremake Britain?
OL,6,FBut the potential tax change that
OL,7,Finterests me most - because it's all
OL,8,Fabout whether Starmer's government
OL,9,Fputs wooing the right-wing media above
OL,10,For below his supposed fundamental
OL,11,Fconvictions - is whether Reeves
OL,12,Fimposes the fuel duty escalator for
OL,13,Fthe first time since 2010.
OL,15,FYou would think that this government
OL,16,Fwould raise fuel duty by the rate of
OL,17,Finflation or more, given that it badly
OL,18,Fneeds the #1.5 billion or so it would
OL,19,Fyield, and based on its climate change
OL,20,Fprinciples.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/13
