OL,3,CHow will Reeves' budget reset and
OL,4,Cremake Britain?
OL,6,FBut there is a powerful motorists'
OL,7,Flobby that - via its friends in the
OL,8,Ftabloid press - has managed to put the
OL,9,Fescalator on ice for well over a
OL,10,Fdecade.
OL,12,FIf Reeves chooses not to increase fuel
OL,13,Fduty, she may claim that's because
OL,14,Fshe's anxious about hurting small
OL,15,Fbusinesses.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/13
