OL,3,CHow will Reeves' budget reset and
OL,4,Cremake Britain?
OL,6,FWhat she should say is that she is
OL,7,Fanxious about hurting small businesses
OL,8,Fmore than would otherwise be the case
OL,9,F- because it is the small business
OL,10,Fsector that will struggle most with
OL,11,Fthe significant cost increments from
OL,12,Fher NI change, a big rise in the
OL,13,Fnational minimum or living wage and
OL,14,FAngela Rayner's reforms to employees'
OL,15,Fcontractual rights.
OL,17,FAt best the small business sector will
OL,18,Fstagnate. At worst, many small
OL,19,Fbusinesses - that have been barely
OL,20,Fprofitable for years - will collapse.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/13
